{"text": "Cloud computing ek modern technology hai jo internet ke zariye computing services provide karti hai. Yeh users ko allow karti hai ke woh apne data aur applications ko remote servers par store kar sakein instead of local computers par. Cloud computing ke teen main types hain: public cloud, private cloud, aur hybrid cloud. Companies aur individuals cloud services use karte hain kyunke yeh cost-effective aur scalable solution hai. Cloud computing ke fayde mein accessibility, flexibility, aur automatic updates shamil hain jo traditional computing methods mein available nahi hote. Major cloud service providers jaise Amazon Web Services, Microsoft Azure, aur Google Cloud Platform ne is industry ko revolutionize kiya hai. Cloud computing ne businesses ko enable kiya hai ke woh apne operations ko efficiently manage kar sakein aur remote work ko possible banaya hai. Is technology ne data backup aur disaster recovery ko bhi asaan bana diya hai kyunke information multiple locations par stored hoti hai. Future mein cloud computing aur bhi advanced ho jaegi aur artificial intelligence ke saath integrate ho kar new possibilities create karegi."}
